description:
Designed to make progressing through the game easier, the Big Game Summoning Set set includes 5 fish-summoning rods for use in Ace Angler +, new outfits, and Tickets to unlock new fish for your aquarium.

Content includes:
• Aloha Outfit Set
• Apron Outfit Set
• Fish-Summoning Normal Rod: Salmon Rod
• Fish-Summoning Super Rod: Common Octopus Rod
• Fish-Summoning Ultra Rod: Frilled Shark Rod
• Fish-Summoning Legend Rod: Megalodon Rod
• Fish-Summoning Devil Rod: Mosasaurus Rod
• 3 Normal Tickets
• 1 Rare Ticket
name: Ace Angler: Fishing Spirits Big Game Summoning Set
